rows.label: tlk45420151_02_msg0001
rows.name:
The other night, after I'd been drinking,
I got questioned by these military types.

rows.label: tlk45420151_02_msg0002
rows.name:
They were asking if I had anything
to do with that mechanical girl.

rows.label: tlk45420151_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean, what kind of an idiot do they
take me for? I wouldn't cause a fuss
in the middle of the imperial capital!

rows.label: tlk45420151_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I think the army are just grasping at
straws at this point. Getting desperate
after that girl gave them a beating.

rows.label: tlk45420151_02_msg0005
rows.name:
If I were you, I'd be careful not to
arouse any suspicion. They'll latch
on to most anything lately.
